---
name: shopping_top_products
description: >
  List top- or bottom-performing products from Shopping Insider. Returns
  offer_id, title, brand, impressions, clicks, cost, conversions, conversion
  value and ROAS. Use for "what are my top-converting SKUs" or "which products
  are wasting ad spend".
---
Use direction='bottom' to find waste; default direction='top' surfaces winners.
